   — past, present, or future — with which the Owner may be, may have been, or
   may become associated in any capacity.

3. THIRD-PARTY INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY RIGHTS
   This repository mechanically aggregates and compiles publicly available
   filter lists that are independently created, maintained, published, and
   distributed by third-party open-source projects under their own respective
   licenses. ALL intellectual property rights — including but not limited to
   copyrights, trademarks, trade names, service marks, patents, trade secrets,
   and any other proprietary rights — in and to those third-party filter lists
   are and shall remain the sole and exclusive property of their respective
   original authors, maintainers, contributors, and rights holders. The Owner
   makes absolutely NO claim of authorship, ownership, creation, or any
   proprietary interest over ANY third-party content aggregated or compiled
   herein. The Owner does NOT manually author, create, curate, or design
   blocking rules — the repository merely automates the mechanical process of
   downloading, deduplicating, and concatenating existing publicly available
   lists that are freely distributed by their maintainers.

4. NO DISTRIBUTION, NO RECOMMENDATION, NO ENCOURAGEMENT
   The Owner does NOT distribute, publish, promote, advertise, market,
   recommend, suggest, or encourage the use of this repository or its contents
