   updates for third-party use, and does NOT operate this as a service,
   product, or offering of any kind. Any third party who independently
   discovers and accesses this repository does so entirely at their own
   initiative, volition, risk, and responsibility, without any invitation,
   solicitation, or encouragement from the Owner.

5. NO COMMERCIAL USE — NO REVENUE — NO BUSINESS PURPOSE
   This project is strictly and exclusively non-commercial in nature and
   purpose. It generates no revenue of any kind — no advertising revenue, no
   subscription fees, no donations, no sponsorships, no affiliate income, and
   no monetary compensation of any form. It is not used in connection with any
   commercial activity, business purpose, competitive advantage, or economic
